WEBVTT


00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.778
AfD gains strongly in the east

00:00:01.779 --> 00:00:04.144
and continues its upward trend nationwide.

00:00:04.513 --> 00:00:06.246
According to a recent survey, 

00:00:06.246 --> 00:00:06.998
the AfD leads

00:00:06.999 --> 00:00:08.159
in the east of Germany

00:00:08.160 --> 00:00:10.016
with 8 percent points ahead of the Union.

00:00:10.593 --> 00:00:14.180
Compared to the federal elections 2,021

00:00:14.181 --> 00:00:15.328
records the AfD

00:00:15.353 --> 00:00:18.223
an increase of 13 comma 1 percent,

00:00:18.480 --> 00:00:21.893
while the CDU gained only 6 points 9 percent.

00:00:21.993 --> 00:00:24.446
Especially the parties of the traffic light coalition

00:00:24.447 --> 00:00:25.681
are punished,

00:00:25.682 --> 00:00:29.247
with the chancellor SPD losing 12 commas 1 percent.

00:00:29.680 --> 00:00:31.750
The Greens keep it easy in the east,

00:00:31.751 --> 00:00:34.733
while the FDP slips to 4 percent.

00:00:34.896 --> 00:00:38.702
With regard to the state elections 2,024 in 3 OST

00:00:38.703 --> 00:00:40.551
States of Saxony,

00:00:40.552 --> 00:00:41.636
Thuringia, 

00:00:41.636 --> 00:00:42.721
Brandenburg

00:00:42.722 --> 00:00:44.181
could the AfD high

00:00:44.182 --> 00:00:47.225
make it difficult to form majorities and coalitions.

00:00:47.560 --> 00:00:48.810
Remarkable is,

00:00:48.811 --> 00:00:51.261
that the AfD has never yet been the strongest force

00:00:51.262 --> 00:00:52.740
was in a major election,

00:00:52.961 --> 00:00:55.179
but this could change in the next year.

00:00:55.641 --> 00:00:57.930
The nationwide Forza survey shows,

00:00:57.931 --> 00:00:58.771
that the AfD

00:00:58.772 --> 00:01:02.240
also rises to 22 percent at the federal level,

00:01:02.261 --> 00:01:04.999
while The Greens lose one percentage point.

00:01:05.360 --> 00:01:08.626
The SPD remains unchanged at 14 percent,

00:01:08.773 --> 00:01:11.006
the Union leads with 30 percent

00:01:11.133 --> 00:01:13.486
and the FDP achieves 5 percent.

00:01:13.733 --> 00:01:14.693
At 4 percent, 

00:01:14.693 --> 00:01:15.653
the left could

00:01:15.654 --> 00:01:17.787
miss the entry into the Bundestag.
